      • execute

        IntLiveResultSet execute(long pid,
                         java.lang.String cmd)
        implementation of this method should execute the command cmd and with the pid specified. cmd should not be contain relative paths. each and every path should be absolute. call of this method should not take long time to terminate. this method must return immediately. this method can start parallel threads which can modify the resultSet return by this method.
        Parameters:
        pid - Program ID for which the command is going to be executed.
        cmd - Command for execution.
        Returns:
        IntLiveResultSet, containing the result of command.
